Latzel 1880: "Tarnowaner Wald bei Görz" = Trnovo Forest Plateau, near Gorica; also reported as "Küstenlande" = Eastern Adriatic coastal region
) and in the label associated with two syntypes (“Tarnowaner Wald”). The second type locality is indicated in the original description ( Latzel 1880 ) only as " Kärnten " (= Carinthia ), but a single locality "Loiblthal" is indicated by the same author when treating the fauna of Carinthia ( Latzel 1885 ).

